f5cbe8d4d2685","tid":342794,"uid":48733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T02:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搞到一鑊泡，俾MI6雪藏<br />\n最尾去美國<br />\n套戲成本3千萬美元，頭周末收千八，計埋海外回到本，睇佢有無續集</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實佢千曬三方：美、英、蘇？佢先係雙面？</blockquote><br />\n我諗係，睇佢個串款，不過佢都好搏命</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺佢係屈James McAvoy 係雙面 <br />\n佢係內鬼但不是雙面<br />\n<br />\n好搏命添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然無john wick 個種遇神殺神個種感覺<br />\n但多左份感性 <br />\n其實佢應該對法國spy 有好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528047e051f9b81d86878908141d6e65234903f5","tid":342794,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T02:23:35.000Z","msg":"兩個都有露點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4803202817ca4cfaad0b86aedfff1becd8e58e81","tid":342794,"uid":48733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T02:23:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩個都有露點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c04995b19977837d6071b8f5270d6012a334e03","tid":342794,"uid":48733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T02:24:38.000Z","msg":"開場 Charlize 浸水個幕似John Wick <br />\n但型到爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2525fe03f0cb28ca800b60b13a51825f7978e2","tid":342794,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T02:35:06.000Z","msg":"加咁多文戲 但交代劇情又咁廢 無乜伏線又想加爆點突兀到<br />\n不如好似jw咁打到尾算啦 除左動作場面睇到訓著"},{"pid":"e8f189f9d2b65ac1ba7eced05a799cce0a29b912","tid":342794,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"一take過打鬥精彩，甚至應該全年最佳，但導演開故仔能力有點弱，尤其是法國妹條線交待得唔好。<br />\n整體有D悶和寡。我自己就覺得女主似係英美間諜，而占士係雙面。"},{"pid":"fd265b8cbf1d8e956a1f5df3f7bc37c0a1485326","tid":342794,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:05:31.000Z","msg":"好憎James McAvoy做咩唔似咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw畫面ok靚但故事的確係弱點"},{"pid":"107f47732e427d775f7942fe289483a7328d23cf","tid":342794,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好憎James McAvoy做咩唔似咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw畫面ok靚但故事的確係弱點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拍左十幾年都係扮型。<br />\n南非影后做戲都麻麻"},{"pid":"df19c254ed90f5b1f0694e945105fa39d4ae3697","tid":342794,"uid":48733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加咁多文戲 但交代劇情又咁廢 無乜伏線又想加爆點突兀到<br />\n不如好似jw咁打到尾算啦 除左動作場面睇到訓著</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我又覺得文戲可以接受"},{"pid":"9da414c5a68f0da7f9344581064df09bdf977876","tid":342794,"uid":48733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:16:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一take過打鬥精彩，甚至應該全年最佳，但導演開故仔能力有點弱，尤其是法國妹條線交待得唔好。<br />\n整體有D悶和寡。我自己就覺得女主似係英美間諜，而占士係雙面。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得女主角先係雙面<br />\n<br />\n占士係內鬼only"},{"pid":"eeb930389af568383dfcef7cccee78c9d99d561f","tid":342794,"uid":27616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T08:50:26.000Z","msg":"佢真正身份係美？<br />\n佢最尾上左cia飛機"},{"pid":"d6721c301dd777f8743090ee375d1380b483c99d","tid":342794,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T08:53:09.000Z","msg":"望遠鏡應該知道邊個係雙面？"},{"pid":"106bd69437d8753e56629805ac0c73a84447a532","tid":342794,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:29:30.000Z","msg":"啲剪接真係一撚流<br />\n<br />\n其實佢係咪即係美國派出去嘅雙面"},{"pid":"d2a3b24f8acc85ba2fe8649471bd17eab371a3b2","tid":342794,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:36:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲剪接真係一撚流<br />\n<br />\n其實佢係咪即係美國派出去嘅雙面</blockquote><br />\n但係佢又咁落力救望遠鏡？<br />\n望遠鏡死左咪冇名單，冇人知佢係雙面？"},{"pid":"909eb0be4025af0c7cefd2af8d27f3ac7448fb0f","tid":342794,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲剪接真係一撚流<br />\n<br />\n其實佢係咪即係美國派出去嘅雙面</blockquote><br />\n但係佢又咁落力救望遠鏡？<br />\n望遠鏡死左咪冇名單，冇人知佢係雙面？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得有D唔合理既，如果影后多重間諜final boss，<br />\n根本唔駛搏死老命保護望遠鏡，<br />\nJohn Goodman 都有話唔信人可以記到咁多資料"},{"pid":"decc06d152666861f23319e52b21c80a473d15e4","tid":342794,"uid":58008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T09:57:41.000Z","msg":"仲以為睇唔明係我問題<br />\n套戲劇情真係交代到1999 未試過睇戲咁無頭緒<br />\n打鬥戲好真實 1take過果part真係比滿分<br />\n去到最尾邊個打邊個我都係完全唔撚明, 到底最後邊個叫&quot;贏左&quot;?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他懸疑片都無依套咁難明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91e1b6b7a4f261b6935e67424085880aadf0e48","tid":342794,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:05:45.000Z","msg":"個劇情真係一個敗筆<br />\n<br />\n有啲唔清唔楚<br />\n<br />\n交代唔到<br />\n<br />\n不過整體黎講都好好睇"},{"pid":"c10c5e6075cb5c1f8d57290af516a879419ac4d2","tid":342794,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:09:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啲剪接真係一撚流<br />\n<br />\n其實佢係咪即係美國派出去嘅雙面</blockquote><br />\n但係佢又咁落力救望遠鏡？<br />\n望遠鏡死左咪冇名單，冇人知佢係雙面？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得有D唔合理既，如果影后多重間諜final boss，<br />\n根本唔駛搏死老命保護望遠鏡，<br />\nJohn Goodman 都有話唔信人可以記到咁多資料</blockquote><br />\n會唔會想救望遠鏡<br />\n<br />\n係因為想攞埋其他特工嘅資料<br />\n<br />\n即係嗰陣隻錶未有線索係邊<br />\n<br />\n所以望遠鏡就係唯一嘅名單"},{"pid":"18adc5c0fa9f3165cabe1213aedac979c03d98e1","tid":342794,"uid":15045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T11:25:29.000Z","msg":"一鏡果段真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad49ba250a61b064645ec95cf4d7299338290b3","tid":342794,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T12:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一鏡果段真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知take左幾多次，應該都唔容許太多。<br />\n可能排得多關係，開頭樓梯係好勁，<br />\n到入房感覺少少甩，但都係好犀利"}]}